<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<!--<h4>First Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī śakavaruṣaṁbu 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>lu 1133 dagu pramōdu 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>tha saṁvatsaramuna śrīma 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>tu melugaṁṭi komaranāya 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ka dēvara <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> nāya 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ka betanāya <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> nāya 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>kulu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> du <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/>ya jiyala <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="9"/>miga <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ha 
<lb n="10"/>rā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="11"/>ḍaina <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="12"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="13"/>dukēśvaramu sthānamu 
<lb n="14"/>naṁdrikūṭamu guḍlubhī 
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ma jiyadanaceti dana 
<lb n="16"/>munana kaḷaśa nirmāṇamu 
<lb n="17"/>gāṁjeyeṁcina Ītrikū 
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ṭamu Aṁgabhōga raṁgabhō 
<lb n="19" break="no"/>ga dūpa dīpa naivēdyamu 
<lb n="20" break="no"/>laku mupai maṭlu velivo 
<lb n="21" break="no"/>la mācaṁdrārkasthāyamu 
<lb n="22" break="no"/>gā nicciri Ī dharmmanakevva 
<lb n="23" break="no"/>rēnanukūlulaina vāriki 
<lb n="24"/>sarvva saṁddulagubratikū 
<lb n="25" break="no"/>lulairīniṁdamasapadakṣa 
<lb n="26" break="no"/>yamagu dēvadattigoniko 
<lb n="27" break="no"/>ni danamalamūtrādu 
<lb n="28" break="no"/>lu dānabhakṣiṁcinavāḍu 
</p>

<!--<h4>Third Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="29"/>svadattāṁ paradatta vā 
<lb n="30" break="no"/>yō harērbhūmivu tiha 
<lb n="31" break="no"/>sā pacyate mahāyo 
<lb n="32" break="no"/>ṁnarake kālayakṣa 
<lb n="31" break="no"/>ya datnānnadāna gōśvā 
<lb n="30"/>dṛssarvvabhūmiprada 
<lb n="31" break="no"/>yasta <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tasmārdami pra <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> nena rājābhavati sarvvadā 
</p>

